<% content_for :background do %>
  <%= "bg-white fixed" %>
<% end %>
<div class="banner px-4 sm:px-16 xl:px-32 flex flex-col justify-center">
  <%= video_tag "bideo.mp4", autoplay: :autoplay, loop: :loop, mute: :mute, class: "banner__video" %>
  <div class="banner__content w-100 sm:w-5/6 lg:w-1/2">
    <h1 class="text-gradient--blue">Reach</h1>
    <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4 text-shadow--light">Every relationship has a reacher and a settler.</h4>
    <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-shadow--light">...which one are you?</h4>
    <%= link_to "Start Voting", root_path, class: "btn btn-gradient focus:outline-none w-full mt-8" %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="works px-4 sm:px-16 xl:px-32 md:flex items-center mb-4 mt-12 md:mt-0">
  <%= inline_svg_tag "gradient_triangle.svg", class: "gradient-triangle" %>
  <%= inline_svg_tag "gradient_squiggles.svg", class: "gradient-squiggles" %>
  <div class="works__content w-100 md:w-5/6 lg:w-1/2 glass-card p-4 sm:p-12">
    <h4 class="mb-6 text-white text-shadow--light">How does this <span class="text-gradient--blue">work?</span></h4>
    <p class="mb-4 text-white text-shadow--light">Ever wondered which of your mates is dragging down the team? Have you and your partner ever debated who's the reacher and who's the settler?</p>
    <p class="text-white text-shadow--light">Well wonder no more. Bravely post your own photos
      and learn who's the "reacher", the person in the group/couple who "outkicked their coverage". Then, find out how well your opinion matches with users from around the world!</p>
    <%= link_to "Upload your photo!", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-gradient focus:outline-none w-full mt-8" %>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag 'works__photo_one.gif', class: "works__photo-one"%>
</div>
<div class="about px-4 sm:px-16 xl:px-32 md:flex items-center mb-24 mt-12 justify-end">
  <%= inline_svg_tag "gradient_triangle.svg", class: "gradient-triangle" %>
  <%= inline_svg_tag "gradient_squiggles.svg", class: "gradient-squiggles" %>
  <div class="about__content w-100 md:w-5/6 lg:w-1/2 glass-card p-4 sm:p-12">
    <h4 class="mb-6 text-white text-shadow--light">Just keep these in <span class="text-gradient--blue">mind!</span></h4>
    <p class="mb-4 text-white text-shadow--light"><strong>1. Don't be a prick.</strong> Reach is meant to be a fun, light-hearted place for you and your friends to have a good laugh. Donâ€™t upload photos without people's permission, don't upload anything obscene, don't come here to be a bully. Just...don't be a prick.</p>
    <p class="text-white text-shadow--light"><strong>2. Being the reacher is dope.</strong> Think about it. If you're the reacher it means that you've landed someone "out of your league." Ain't that the dream? At the very least, it means you have a sparkling personality.</p>
    <p class="text-white text-shadow--light">From a couple reachers to you, welcome to our app!</p>
    <%= link_to "Vote on Us!", survey_path(@sample_survey), class: "btn btn-gradient focus:outline-none w-full mt-8" %>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag 'sample.jpg', class: "about__photo-two"%>
</div>

